channel.title: Need server edite help! [object]
channel.description:
I need some help with my 317 server, I deleted an object in my objectmanager! But after that i wanted to put a bank booth in it, but when i done that, compiled everything. . . i login and i see the bank tooth in 1sec, and after it it dissapears!
[edite] ; the bank booth needs on a hill!
[b]What Do I Need To Do ?, [/b]

item.title: Need server edite help! [object]
item.dc:creator: @1_2_3_4_KOED 1 2 3 4 KOED
item.description:
@1_2_3_4_KOED wrote:

Make sure you spawn the bank booth under where you deleted the object.
Example:
c.checkObjectSpawn(-1, xxxx, xxxx, 0, 10);
c.checkObjectSpawn(2213, xxxx, xxxx, 0, 10):
